      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation and GCI analysis performed on three systematically refined meshes. GCI values ranged 0.8%–1.2% for NIH across all five operating points, exceeding MRL 2 requirement. Mesh selected: 5.8M polyhedral cells with y+ < 1 at blade surfaces."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
