      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental protocol specifies flow rates measured by Coriolis meter (±0.5%), rotational speed by optical encoder (±2 RPM), and fluid temperature controlled at 37±0.5°C. CFD boundary conditions derived directly from experimental measurements; discrepancy < 2% for all BCs."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
