      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump — same geometry class as COU device. Operating points span COU envelope (2.5–7.0 L/min, 2500–3500 RPM). Blood analog fluid (glycerol-water, matched viscosity) used per FDA guidance. Geometric fidelity confirmed by CT scan comparison."
